Module new_project
Package users

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
users.User
users.Staff
public class Staff extends User
Represents a staff member of the fast-food restaurant. Each staff member has attributes such as staff ID, name, role (Admin, Manager, or Staff), gender, age, branch ID, and password. The class also provides methods for password management and accessing staff details.
